Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.01,0:26:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.13,0:26:35.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何だよ いきなり！\N謝りに来たんじゃないのかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.03,0:26:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you come here to apologize?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.92,0:26:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sucks to be you!{like this(kevo)lol, couldn't think of anything here}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.97,0:26:39.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっかんべー
