Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.81,0:26:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey wait up Mion! Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.35,0:26:48.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魅音）ヘヘヘッ やなこったー！
